---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Careers at Severino Realty"
  description="Join the Severino Realty team and build a rewarding career in real estate. We offer mentorship, growth, and a supportive environment.">

  <section class="py-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Careers at Severino Realty</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
      We’re always looking for talented individuals to join our growing team.
      Whether you’re a seasoned agent or just starting your career, Severino Realty
      offers training, mentorship, and a collaborative environment.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Current Openings</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
      We currently do not have open positions. However, we welcome proactive applicants!
      Please send your CV and a short cover letter to
      <a href="mailto:careers@severino.com" class="text-cta hover:text-accent">
        careers@severino.com
      </a>
      for future consideration.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Why Work With Us?</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Competitive commission structures</li>
      <li>Continuous training and professional development</li>
      <li>Supportive team culture</li>
      <li>Opportunities for growth in a dynamic industry</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
